title: Any Move Is Possible: A Free-Agency Preview | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
The trade between the Giants and Browns (00:30), Trey Flowers and other available defensive linemen (06:15), Earl Thomas and a crowded safety market (18:30), Le’Veon Bell’s fluctuating value (29:30), where Nick Foles ranks among free-agent QBs (44:30), and more.
  
Hosts: Robert Mays and Kevin Clark
